
This simple web application provides users with an easy-to-understand overview of the key characteristics of soil that make it suitable for plant growth. Through a clean and visually appealing layout, it highlights important soil properties such as texture, pH level, moisture, organic matter content, and aeration. By presenting these factors in a clear list format, the application educates users about what type of soil conditions are ideal for healthy plant development. The design uses calming green tones to evoke a natural feel, making the information both accessible and inviting for gardeners, students, or anyone interested in plant care.


